```

### Testing
```bash
npm test                       # Unit tests
npm run test-cypress           # Cypress E2E tests (interactive)
npm run test-cypress-headless  # Cypress E2E tests (CI)
USE_SCENARIO_INFRA=true npm run test-playwright -- --project=scenario  # Scenario tests
npm run test-playwright -- --project=setup --project=Gating            # Gating tests
